Class Priest

  • java.lang.Object
    • PlayerCharacter
      • Priest

  • public class Priest
extends PlayerCharacter
    This is the Priest character class that contains a couple of basic heal spells and a general growth rate each time the character levels up.
    Author:
    Matt Hendrick

        public void cureLight()
        The first spell the priest learns after the initial spell. It is designed to cost more, but will cure the character of more damage than the first level spell.
